{"tid":2245973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"70歲李司棋着黑色魚網絲襪勁搶鏡　網民大讚性感又美麗：人比花嬌","createTime":"2020-10-16T15:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T09:29:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e56a7c810f0116ec62ae774bb07c2a74bd4e4406","tid":2245973,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:57:19.000Z","msg":"上月底剛過70歲生日的李司棋不時在社交平台更新近況，心境年青的她一時分享美食，一時又上載行山的照片，生活非常充實。不過數到網民最Like的，一定是司棋姐的「黑絲」相，事關每隔一排，她就會穿上心愛的黑色絲襪並拍照與大家開心Share。<br />\n<br />\n日前，司棋姐就在IG上載了與美麗花朵的合照，並寫着：「朋友送的胡姬花，放了個多星期依然盛放，襟擺，襟睇！」之不過網民的焦點都落在她的黑色魚網絲襪上，更大讚司棋姐人比花嬌：「司棋姐和花一樣美麗」、「性感黑絲美腿」、「花美，人美，心情美」。"},{"pid":"9db6ff7420635c512b0123bb3198b8d8a692572e","tid":2245973,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393909414412685312851439.jpeg/3IanPDZ8nALiVXq_BMFv5umnyq-jF7RVTC8puEwvKbg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393909414412685312851439.jpeg%2F3IanPDZ8nALiVXq_BMFv5umnyq-jF7RVTC8puEwvKbg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f2c15ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393909661545271296593407.jpeg/Hz19DJjdlFLUNgUosqNX07mKudI_0K_djh2a3o4dmt4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393909661545271296593407.jpeg%2FHz19DJjdlFLUNgUosqNX07mKudI_0K_djh2a3o4dmt4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8276b099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201016/393909664007458816102354.jpeg/i9zQWoT1sYvT3EzN4gQ5AZ4zfUUh2fUgkELuepBC7no?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201016%2F393909664007458816102354.jpeg%2Fi9zQWoT1sYvT3EzN4gQ5AZ4zfUUh2fUgkELuepBC7no%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8da12214&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5c49c021d26be6b6b79a9a6427b35b783c221d4","tid":2245